Activate or Deactivate a Company. Set isActive=false to deactivate (record is NOT deleted). Set isActive=true to reactivate.

Request Body: { "isActive": true | false }

Response: { "message": "Company activated/deactivated successfully", "company": {...} }

Distribution report for petrol advances (Field Selectors).

## Response Shape:
```json
{
  "groupBy": "month",
  "timeSeries": [
    { "label": "Apr 2026", "totalAmount": 4500, "count": 6 },
    { "label": "Mar 2026", "totalAmount": 3200, "count": 4 }
  ],
  "perSelector": [
    { "_id": "...", "selectorName": "Prashant Desai", "mobile": "9876543210", "totalAmount": 2500, "count": 3 }
  ]
}
```

Distribution report for diesel advances (Eicher + Pickup drivers).

## Response Shape:
```json
{
  "groupBy": "month",
  "timeSeries": [
    { "label": "Apr 2026", "totalAmount": 12000, "count": 15 },
    { "label": "Mar 2026", "totalAmount": 9800, "count": 12 }
  ],
  "perDriver": [
    { "_id": "...", "driverName": "Sidhu Wagh", "mobile": "9876543210", "role": "driver eicher", "vehicleNumbers": ["MH45AF8299"], "totalAmount": 5000, "count": 6 }
  ]
}
```

**perDriver** always sorted by highest advance total. Includes all vehicle numbers used by that driver.
